<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Re: GMS just make things worse. Got suspended for no reason.</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois.cgi?Selki">Selki</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 12:39 a.m. 15/7/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Re: GMS just make things worse. Got suspended for no reason.<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/datel.gif" width=46 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dateblnk.gif" width=100 height=22 border=0><img src="http://www.everworld.net/images/dater.gif" width=306 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/forum/tunare.cgi?read=111" TARGET=_self>GMS just make things worse. Got suspended for no reason.</A> (Calindor)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#F4D99F FACE=arial>
<P>Sup calindor i got my Oracle Robes like i said i was =) BUT......i too was suspended for some dumb stuff and did not get to voice my opinion...iam not taking this plz join me friend i am a

<BR>Economist and i know that they can not do some things they do bc its illeagal here is a list
<P>1 - Invading or monitoring private conversations...thier disclaimer says they reserve the right to monitor the "chat" the definition of chat does NOT include Private conversations
<P>2 - In the world of Ever Quest you are Guilty untill prioven innocence ....once again this violates the constitution and is illegal to promote in the US
<P>3 - They breached there contract ....the guides and GM's have specific lists to follow when dealing with a situation.... they can not just ignore someone and call it a Handled Problem.
<P>4 - They call Bug Explotation a fault when infact it is the fault of the tech dept...... they had a beta and should have fixed the bugs....Are you telling me im paying for a game that is Bugged and incomplete?....Roleplaying is thier excuse for not allowing bug exploits...but i say if you really want to make the game real ask your self this? does everyone make a cool mill a yr? does everyone know
<P>how to get to the top? the answer is no.....you can not expect to make a game to be fair to all when ther are just some that have can achieve and some that cant......as far as the Bug Exploit goes if a monster was attacking me i would DEFINATELY find a way to trap or trick it so i would not take dmg. especially since im a wizard.
<P>I hope some of these show others how this game is being run corruptly and disorderly!
<BR>FEEL FREE TO COMMENT
<P>---------------------------------------------
<P>Selki Wizard on Tunare
